snippet.title: Battle, Spin, and Win in Pokémon Duel!
snippet.description:
http://bit.ly/2kphcxz
Build your party of Pokémon figures and play against your friends in Pokémon Duel! Now available on Apple and Android devices. Visit our site to learn more about this game!
